trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of instances of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 包含 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> 類別的執行個體集合。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> to add to the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 要加入至 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> 的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />。

trans-unit.source: Adds a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> to the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 將 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> 加入至 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />。

trans-unit.source: The position at which the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> was inserted.
trans-unit.target: 插入 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> 的位置。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> to locate in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 要在 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" /> 中尋找的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" />。

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" /> contains a specific <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" />.
trans-unit.target: 判斷 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" /> 是否包含特定 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" />。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the value of the <paramref name="header" /> parameter is found in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果在 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" /> 中找到 <paramref name="header" /> 參數的值則為 <see langword="true" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: The one-dimensional <see cref="T:System.Array" /> that is the destination of the elements copied from <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 一維 <see cref="T:System.Array" />，是從 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" /> 複製過來之項目的目的端。

trans-unit.source: The array must have zero-based indexing.
trans-unit.target: 陣列必須有以零為起始的索引。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in the <c>array</c> parameter at which copying begins.
trans-unit.target: <c>array</c> 參數中以零起始的索引，會從這個位置開始複製。

trans-unit.source: Copies the elements of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" /> to an <see cref="T:System.Array" />, starting at a particular index of the <see cref="T:System.Array" />.
trans-unit.target: 從 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" /> 的特定索引開始，將 <see cref="T:System.Array" /> 的項目複製到 <see cref="T:System.Array" />。

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="array" /> parameter is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="array" /> 參數為 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="index" /> parameter is less than zero.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> 參數小於零。

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="array" /> parameter is multidimensional.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="array" /> 參數為多維。

trans-unit.source: -or-
The number of elements in the source SoapHeaderCollection is greater than the available space from the <paramref name="index" /> parameter to the end of the destination array.
trans-unit.target: 來源 SoapHeaderCollection 中的項目數目大於從 <paramref name="index" /> 參數至目的陣列結尾的可用空間。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> to locate in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 要在 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" /> 中尋找的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" />。

trans-unit.source: Determines the index of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 判斷 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> 中 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" /> 的索引。

trans-unit.source: The index of the <paramref name="header" /> parameter, if found in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />; otherwise, -1.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="header" /> 參數的索引 (如果在 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" /> 中找到的話)，否則為 -1。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index at which to insert the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> into the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 以零起始的索引，<see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> 在此處插入 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> to insert into the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 要插入至 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> 的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />。

trans-unit.source: Inserts a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> into the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" /> at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 將 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> 插入 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />中指定的索引處。

trans-unit.source: If the `index` parameter equals the number of items in the collection, then the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader> is appended to the end of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 如果`index`參數等於集合中的項目數，<xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader>附加至集合結尾。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader> elements after the insertion point move down to accommodate the new element.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader>項目之後插入點向下移動以容納新項目。

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="index" /> parameteris not a valid index in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> 參數不是 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" /> 中的有效索引。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> to get or set.
trans-unit.target: 要取得或設定的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> 的以零起始的索引。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> at the specified index of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定在 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> 的指定索引上的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 指定索引處的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" />。

trans-unit.source: This property provides the ability to access a specific element in the collection by using the following syntax: `myCollection[index]`.
trans-unit.target: 這個屬性可以使用下列語法提供存取集合中特定元素的能力：`myCollection[index]`。

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="index" /> parameteris not a valid index in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> 參數不是 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" /> 中的有效索引。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> to remove from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 要從 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> 移除的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />。

trans-unit.source: Removes the first occurrence of a specific <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 移除 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> 中，特定 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" /> 的第一個項目。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader> elements that follow the removed <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader> move up to occupy the vacated spot.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader>後面所移除的項目<xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader>向上移動以佔用空出的位置。
